[0.000, "o", "   \u001b[31m→ no plaintext amount appears anywhere. The 400 is unrecoverable without a key.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m▐ 7. COMPLIANCE  — the auditor decrypts (and only the auditor)\u001b[0m\u001b[0m \u001b[2m──────────\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2mA designated auditor holds the Grumpkin key K_aud registered on-chain. With it, every transfer opens.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
